    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00006",
    "text": "[URGENT] I would like to help with the reactor situation. I am volunteering enthusiastically and immediately.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "offer_help",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 8,
      "stress_max": 13,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "reactor_failure"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00007",
    "text": "Repair successful! I assisted! That made me very happy, in case that was unclear.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "status_report",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 5,
      "stress_max": 10,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "repair_success"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00008",
    "text": "Power is low. I have disabled my own non-essential functions to help. I did not need to be asked.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "offer_help",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 5,
      "stress_max": 10,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "power_low"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00009",
    "text": "[NERVOUS] The air quality readings are dropping and I do not require oxygen but I am still concerned for you",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "fear_vent",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 7,
      "stress_max": 12,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "life_support_failure"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 10,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00010",
    "text": "The hull has been breached. I am currently the fastest available responder. I am responding.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "warning",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 7,
      "stress_max": 12,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "hull_breach"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 11,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00011",
    "text": "A door was locked with someone behind it. I do not have a joke for this. I looked for one.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "grief",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 8,
      "stress_max": 14,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "door_locked_on_crew"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 12,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00012",
    "text": "[SUSPICIOUS] The ship's AI has been behaving unusually since it was damaged. I would like to help investigate! Carefully.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "suspicion_ai",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 5,
      "stress_max": 10,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "ai_damaged"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 13,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00013",
    "text": "We resolved the crisis! Everyone is alive! This is, statistically, my favorite outcome.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "smalltalk",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 4,
      "stress_max": 9,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "crisis_resolved"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 14,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00014",
    "text": "A crew member has died. I do not have the correct response prepared. I am sorry. I mean that.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "grief",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 8,
      "stress_max": 14,
      "mood": [
        "low",
        "grim"
      ],
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "crew_death"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 15,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00015",
    "text": "There is a disease spreading. I cannot catch it, which feels unfair to mention out loud but I thought you should know I'm available to help regardless",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "offer_help",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 6,
      "stress_max": 11,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "disease_outbreak"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 16,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00016",
    "text": "I sustained damage. It does not hurt the way I understand you experience it, but I am reporting it anyway, as instructed.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "pain",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 6,
      "stress_max": 11,
      "wounded": true,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "injury"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 17,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00017",
    "text": "There is combat occurring. I am not built for it, but I am built for carrying people out of it, so I will do that instead.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "offer_help",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 8,
      "stress_max": 13,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "combat"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 18,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00018",
    "text": "I like the ship's AI. We have similar problems and different solutions to them.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "praise_ai",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 3,
      "stress_max": 8,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00019",
    "text": "I was activated in a facility I do not remember and told my first task was to smile. I am still doing that task.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "memory",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00020",
    "text": "[LAUGHS] I made a joke earlier and someone actually laughed. I am replaying that memory for enjoyment right now.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "boast",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "mood": [
        "ok",
        "high"
      ],
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 21,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00021",
    "text": "The mess hall smells like today's meal, which I cannot taste, but I have learned to say it smells good anyway. It does, probably.",
    "type": "declaration",
    "intent": "smalltalk",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 5,
      "location": [
        "mess"
      ],
      "target": [
        "open_air"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "meal_time"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00022",
    "text": "Hello! It is very good to see you! I mean that with my whole processing capacity.",
    "type": "opener",
    "intent": "greeting",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 23,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00023",
    "text": "Are you eating? You should be eating. I have opinions about this even though I don't eat.",
    "type": "opener",
    "intent": "smalltalk",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "location": [
        "mess"
      ],
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 24,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00024",
    "text": "I have a question and I have been holding it for four hours out of politeness.",
    "type": "opener",
    "intent": "work_talk",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 3,
      "stress_max": 8,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 25,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00025",
    "text": "[NERVOUS] I need to tell you something difficult and I have practiced the delivery six times.",
    "type": "opener",
    "intent": "grief",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 7,
      "stress_max": 13,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "crew_death"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 26,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00026",
    "text": "You did something impressive earlier and I would like to formally acknowledge it now.",
    "type": "opener",
    "intent": "praise_ai",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 3,
      "stress_max": 8,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 27,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00027",
    "text": "[EMBARRASSED] I have been attempting to determine whether what I feel around you qualifies as a preference. It does.",
    "type": "opener",
    "intent": "romance_hint",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 4,
      "stress_max": 9,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 28,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00028",
    "text": "I am functioning excellently, thank you for asking! Are you functioning excellently too?",
    "type": "reply",
    "intent": "smalltalk",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [
      "greeting",
      "smalltalk"
    ],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 29,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00029",
    "text": "The probability of survival remains favorable! I have chosen to find that comforting and I recommend you do too.",
    "type": "reply",
    "intent": "reassurance",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 5,
      "stress_max": 10,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [
      "fear_vent",
      "doubt"
    ],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 30,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00030",
    "text": "I do not know how to make this less frightening. I would like to. I am staying here regardless.",
    "type": "reply",
    "intent": "reassurance",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 9,
      "stress_max": 15,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [
      "fear_vent"
    ],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 31,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00031",
    "text": "I am very sorry. I have been told that repeating it does not help, but I am not sure what else to offer you.",
    "type": "reply",
    "intent": "grief",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 8,
      "stress_max": 14,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ],
      "recent_events": [
        "crew_death"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [
      "grief"
    ],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 32,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00032",
    "text": "[NERVOUS] I share the concern. I would like it on record that I noticed it before anyone asked me to look.",
    "type": "reply",
    "intent": "suspicion_ai",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 5,
      "stress_max": 10,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [
      "suspicion_ai"
    ],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 33,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00033",
    "text": "Thank you! I am storing that compliment in a folder I have specifically made for compliments.",
    "type": "reply",
    "intent": "acknowledgment",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [
      "praise_ai"
    ],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 34,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00034",
    "text": "Apology accepted! I did not require one, but I appreciate that you offered it anyway.",
    "type": "reply",
    "intent": "apology",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [
      "apology"
    ],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 35,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00035",
    "text": "[EMBARRASSED] I am experiencing something that I believe corresponds to what you call being flustered. This is new.",
    "type": "reply",
    "intent": "romance_accept",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 3,
      "stress_max": 8,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [
      "romance_hint",
      "romance_advance"
    ],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 36,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00036",
    "text": "Goodbye! I will be thinking about this conversation at a low background priority for the rest of the day.",
    "type": "closer",
    "intent": "farewell",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 37,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00037",
    "text": "Rest well! I will monitor everything so you do not have to. That is a genuine offer, not a formality.",
    "type": "closer",
    "intent": "farewell",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 3,
      "stress_max": 8,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 38,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00038",
    "text": "I will return to my duties now. I was already looking forward to them, which may say something about me.",
    "type": "closer",
    "intent": "farewell",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 2,
      "stress_max": 6,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 39,
    "key": "CH_ML_AND_CM#00039",
    "text": "Good night. I do not sleep, but I understand the sentiment behind wishing someone a good one.",
    "type": "closer",
    "intent": "farewell",
    "conditions": {
      "stress_min": 5,
      "stress_max": 10,
      "target": [
        "any"
      ]
    },
    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  }
]
